The different mixtures of fruits and vegi's will dazzle any appetite.
They also have the most amazing Gluten free muffins.
This place is located in Scottsdale Quarter.
It looks like a tropical hut you would see in the Islands.
The staff is Amazing and very informative.
This is by far a 5 star place.

